text: Ablaberoides dentilabris is a species of beetles in the family Melolonthidae. It is found in Africa, and was discovered by J. W. van Lansberge in 1886.Lansberge J.W. van (1886) Scarabaeides, Buprestides et Cerambycides de l'Afrique occidentale, envoyes au Musee de Leyde par MM.Veth et Van der Kellen (Note XIII), Notes from the Leyden Museum.
